	<h1 class="title">这个巧克力的外包装上，你可以找到巴西热带雨林</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/75281/small/75281.jgp?1425220992" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Julie Wolfson</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-25 14:48:02 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22774/medium/22774.jpg?1456287395" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22774" data-title="《这个巧克力的外包装上，你可以找到巴西热带雨林》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22774/medium/22774.jpg?1456287395" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22774.html?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
